<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">Tile Turnover Rate</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">Quiz · Scrabble Words Finder · Anagram</p>

    <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
      <time datetime="2026-06-15">June 15, 2026</time>
      <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600"></span>
      <span>6 min read</span>
