    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Every Scrabble game has a rhythm — some race through the bag in 12 turns while others grind for 20+. Understanding tile turnover rate helps you control tempo and make strategic decisions about when to play long words versus short defensive plays.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">What Is Tile Turnover Rate?</h2>

    <p>Tile turnover rate is the average number of tiles played per turn. In a standard game with 100 tiles and 12-18 turns per player, the average hovers around 4-5 tiles per turn across both players.</p>

