    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">How Turnover Affects Game Pace</h2>

    <p>The bag holds 100 tiles. After dealing (7 per player = 14), 86 remain. Every tile placed draws a replacement until empty. Higher turnover means the bag empties faster, endgame arrives sooner, and players see more of the total distribution.</p>

