      <p class="text-base text-gray-200">At high turnover, each player sees roughly <span class="text-white font-medium">45 unique tiles</span> (45% of the bag). At low turnover, only about 28 tiles. More tiles seen = more chances for bingo-capable combinations.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">High-Turnover Strategy — Playing for Speed</h2>

    <p>High turnover favours players with strong vocabulary and bingo-spotting skills. By playing 5-7 letter words every turn, you cycle quickly and maximise premium draws.</p>

