        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Behind and need bingos, stronger vocabulary than opponent, board is open, premium tiles still in bag</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏷️ Tactics</p>
