    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Low-Turnover Strategy — Playing for Control</h2>

    <p>Low turnover favours defensive players who want to control the board. Playing 2-3 tile words in tight spaces slows the game, reduces opponent scoring, and makes endgame predictable.</p>

