    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Impact on Bingo Probability</h2>

    <p>The relationship between turnover and bingos is clear: more tiles cycled = more fresh racks = more chances. But there is a subtlety — it is not just volume, it is the quality of your rack leave after each play.</p>

